<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    %= include '_header', title => 'Slapbird APM - the Open-Source observability platform', description => 'Slapbird APM is a Open-Source web-application observability platform for monitoring web applications. Providing insights into application performance, queries, and request times.'
    <body>
        <main style="min-height: 100vh">
            %= include '_nav'
            <section class="hero is-large">
                <div class="hero-body">
                    <div class="container columns is-vcentered">
                        <div class="column is-half">
                            <h1 class="title mb-2">The Free, and Open-Source Perl application observability platform</h1>
                            <ul class="subtitle">
                                <li>Endpoint performance insights</li>
                                <li>Service dependency visualization</li>
                                <li>Query insights</li>
                                <li>and more!</li>
                            </ul>
                            <a href="/login" class="slapbird-button slapbird-is-secondary">Start for free</a>
                            <a href="/getting-started" class="slapbird-button slapbird-is-primary">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="column is-half" style="border-radius: 0.75rem; box-shadow: rgba(149, 157, 165, 0.2) 0px 8px 24px;">
                            <picture class="image is-16by9">
                                <source srcset="/images/hero.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"/>
                                <source srcset="/images/hero_dark.png"  media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"/>
                                <img src="/images/hero.png"/>
                            </picture>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <hr>
            <section class="container">
                <div class="has-text-centered">
                    <h2 class="is-2 title mb-1">Application Monitoring</h2>
                    <h2 class="is-2 title">for Perl web applications</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="container columns mt-6 mb-6">
                    <div class="column is-one-third has-text-centered">
                        <h3 class="is-4 title">Official Support</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Mojolicious</li>
                            <li>Dancer</li>
                            <li>Plack</li>
                            <li>CGI</li>
                            <li>Raku</li>
                            <li>Want a client? Open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/mollusc-labs/slapbird/issues/new" class="slapbird-link">Github</a>!</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column is-one-third has-text-centered">
                        <h3 class="is-4 title">Monitoring</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Application end-points</li>
                            <li>Performance</li>
                            <li>Application errors</li>
                            <li>Database Queries</li>
                            <li>Distributed systems topology</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column is-one-third has-text-centered">
                        <h3 class="is-4 title">Easy set up</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Install the Slapbird user-agent for your application</li>
                            <li>Create your app on <a href="/" class="slapbird-link">slapbirdapm.com</a></li>
                            <li>1 line of code, 1 environment variable</li>
                            <li>Deploy</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <hr>
            <section class="container">
                <div class="has-text-centered">
                    <h2 class="is-2 title mb-1">Our users love Slapbird</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="container columns mt-6 mb-6">
                    <div class="column is-half mr-3">
                        <p class="mb-2 is-size-5">
                            <strong>"</strong>This tool has been helpful. For example, I noticed a lot of 404s for two routes then
                            I remembered... I changed the routing at some point but never set up redirects for
                            old route to new route. Made a small change to add the redirects and the errors that
                            I previously didn't even know about were gone.<strong>"</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p>- <a class="slapbird-link" href="https://github.com/swaggboi">Daniel Bowling</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column is-half flex ml-3" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between">
                        <p class="mb-2 is-size-5">
                            <strong>"</strong>I've been using SlapbirdAPM on my site for a little while now and so far it's been great.
                            It helped me pin point some slow running queries which needed to be reworked.<strong>"</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-auto">- <a class="slapbird-link" href="https://github.com/shamrice">Erik E</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <hr>
            <section class="container">
                <div class="has-text-centered">
                    <h2 class="is-2 title mb-1">Get powerful insights into</h2>
                    <h2 class="is-2 title">your entire request life-cycle</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="container columns mt-6 mb-6">
                    <h3></h3>
                    <div class="column is-half has-text-right">
                        <h3 class="is-4 title">Stay data-driven with insights into</h3>
                        <ul class="is-size-5 has-text-right">
                            <li>Database queries</li>
                            <li>Request call stacks</li>
                            <li>Outages</li>
                            <li>Errors</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column is-half has-text-right">
                        <picture class="image m-auto" style="width: 400px; height: 240px; border-radius: 0.75rem; box-shadow: rgba(149, 157, 165, 0.2) 0px 8px 24px;">
                            <source srcset="/images/query_insights.png" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)"/>
                            <source srcset="/images/query_insights_dark.png"  media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"/>
                            <img src="/images/query_insights.png"/>
                        </picture>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        %= include '_footer'
    </body>
</html>
